Local Char A04BA5235(15)(1..12)
Local Char A04BA5236(15)(1..12)

If clalev([F:BAL])=0  : Local File BALANCE     [BAL]  : Endif
If clalev([F:FIY])=0  : Local File FISCALYEAR  [FIY]  : Endif
If clalev([F:DAE])=0  : Local File GACCENTRYD  [DAE]  : Endif
If clalev([F:HAE])=0  : Local File GACCENTRY   [HAE]  : Endif

#assignar 0.00 a todas as variáveis do mapa de fluxos de capitais
Local Shortint II, III
For II = 5201 To 5236
    For III = 1 To 12
        Assign "A04BA" + num$(II) + "(" + num$(III) + ")" With "0.00"
    Next
Next

Return
